# Testing #
Different situations to ensure correctness.

## normal plot ##
```{r test_unecho_t, echo=TRUE}
plot(rnorm(5))
```
## plot with unecho'd code block ##
```{r test_unecho_f, echo=FALSE}
plot(rnorm(5))
```

## plot with messages and errors ##
```{r test_messages}
my_plot = function(){
  plot(rnorm(5))
  cat('test')
  message('message')
  warning('warning')
  stop('error')
}
my_plot()
```

## multiple plots  ##
```{r test_plots}
plot(rnorm(5))
plot(rnorm(10))
```
